foreignObject.div: Is application git url ssh or http?
Set the git ssh checkout config
Get the git branches over ssh and present them as choice to user to select
Set the git http checkout config
Get the git branches over http and present them as choice to user to select
Git checkout of the application code with the user selected branch
Do you want to run application build?
Run the build_app.sh script in the application code to build the artifact and copy the resulting artifact inside docker folder
Dockerize and push the docker image to container registry
